videos.description: Lamonte Turner throws up a lob on the fast break and Yves Pons elevates to slam it down in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tennessee's Pons rises up to slam alley-oop from Turner) 2019/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee's Pons rises up to slam alley-oop from Turner

videos.description: Jordan Bowden forces teh steal on D.J. Heath then races down the court and takes off from outside the paint to throw down an emphatic jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bowden drops the hammer on massive fast-break jam) 2019/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bowden drops the hammer on massive fast-break jam
